headline: Keysight Recognized with 2025 TSIA STAR Award for Excellence in Omnichannel Customer Experience Optimization
summary: SANTA ROSA, Calif., November 07, 2025--Keysight Technologies, Inc. (NYSE: KEYS) has been named 2025 winner of the TSIA STAR Award for Excellence in Omnichannel Customer Experience Optimization. Presented by the Technology & Services Industry Association (TSIA), the award honors organizations that have demonstrated exceptional achievement in transforming the customer support journey through a fully integrated, multichannel experience.
